properties.Name: FileSecurityType
properties.Description:
The file security type applied to the file.

Ex:
- Vendor private security
- Government classified security
- Purchasing-party responsible security
- For sale to public
- For sale without IDs to public
- For sale to government without ID
- Not for sale
- Not for distribution
